      </div>
      <span class="homepageMain__spacer4">

      </span>
      <span class="homepageMain__spacer1">

      </span>
      <div class="infoCard homepageMain__Card homepageMain__Card--3">
        <h3>Being a part of the Drupal community is important to me. I've been to <a href="http://drupalcamppa.net/">Drupalcamp PA</a>, I'm a member of the <a href="https://www.drupal.org/association">Drupal Association</a>, and I try to contribute and share the knowledge I have with others.</h3>
